    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Devices incorporating a rack or tray and often a seat and hanger, designed for holding clothing and personal effects. Generally placed in a dressing room or bedroom, and intended for gentlemen's clothing rather than ladies'.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
